00:55:34,375 --> 00:55:36,676
that was new IP.

1167
00:55:37,076 --> 00:55:38,277
It was seeking to innovate.

1168
00:55:39,017 --> 00:55:40,498
And it had an uncertain budget.

1169
00:55:40,538 --> 00:55:42,620
It was a large budget, but it was uncertain.

1170
00:55:43,360 --> 00:55:45,501
And between ourselves and the publisher,

1171
00:55:45,541 --> 00:55:46,642
we wanted to understand...

1172
00:55:49,009 --> 00:55:52,792
the, uh, kind of the difference between

1173
00:55:53,552 --> 00:55:55,954
our perceived value of what we'd built

1174
00:55:56,715 --> 00:56:01,098
and, um, uh, and the true value of where it was.

